				<p class="nyt-article-byline">By SIMON ROMERO</p>
				<p class="nyt-article-summary">Dilma Rousseff defeated a centrist challenger, AÃ©cio Neves, in a tumultuous race marked by accusations of corruption, personal insults and heated debates.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="nyt-article-promo">
								<div class="w190">
